758
00:34:01,433 --> 00:34:03,135
That's fair.

759
00:34:05,903 --> 00:34:07,803
Walt is smoking
that filthy cigar

760
00:34:07,805 --> 00:34:08,971
out there on the porch.

761
00:34:08,973 --> 00:34:10,941
Dead and nasty things.

762
