Wasn't easy.

770
00:34:29,227 --> 00:34:30,792
Mmm.

771
00:34:30,794 --> 00:34:32,330
This goddamn fortune.

772
00:34:34,432 --> 00:34:35,964
You know, sometimes I think

773
